* Description

  This repository is for CyanogenMod (4.4.3) on Samsung Galaxy SIV Mini a.k.a Samsung Serranoltexx.
  It's still a work in progress.

* How To Build CyanogenMod (4.4.3) for Samsung Serranoltexx

  - Make a workspace

  $ mkdir -p ~/cyanogen
  $ cd ~/cyanogen


  - Do repo init & sync

  $ repo init -u git://github.com/CyanogenMod/android.git -b cm-11.0


  - Create .repo/local_manifests/roomservice.xml with the following content:

  <?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
  <manifest>
      <project name="OliverG96/android_device_samsung_serranoltex" path="device/samsung/serranoltex" />
      <project name="OliverG96/android_kernel_samsung_serranoltex" path="kernel/samsung/serranoltex" />
      <project name="OliverG96/android_vendor_samsung_serranoltex" path="vendor/samsung/serranoltex" />
  </manifest>

  $ repo sync

  - Setup environment

  $ source build/envsetup.sh
  $ lunch cm_serranoltex-eng


  - Build CyanogenMod (4.4.3)

  $ export USE_CCACHE=1
  $ make -j4 bacon


